'''Trammistan chocolate''' was a type of [[Chocolate/Legends|chocolate]], produced on [[Trammis III/Legends|Trammis III]].<ref name="CSWE">{{CSWECite|III|259|Trammis III}}</ref> It could be used to make [[Trammistan chocolate ice cream]].<ref name="DaD">{{Hyperspace|url=fans/hyperspace/source/dexdiner/index.html|text=Dining at Dex's|int=Dining at Dex's}}</ref>

